{"tid":2419343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生疫市下跌 中共趁機出手  中資買起英17私校 政黨促阻文化滲透","createTime":"2021-02-23T09:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T09:25:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d213ef40160e0745895f75cec301beefa6533e3","tid":2419343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210223/FHBLYGDE4ZEGJGBTX7T4UKJYKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210223%2FFHBLYGDE4ZEGJGBTX7T4UKJYKI%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=095b3649\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210223%2FFHBLYGDE4ZEGJGBTX7T4UKJYKI%2F&h=8d966817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210223/FHBLYGDE4ZEGJGBTX7T4UKJYKI/</a><br />\n<br />\n學生疫市下跌 中共趁機出手 <br />\n中資買起英17私校 政黨促阻文化滲透<br />\n<br />\n英國媒體統計發現，當地至少17間私人學校近年被中資財團收購，一半的財團擁有者是中共高級黨員，有集團更直認收購是響應「一帶一路」的號召，報道又指武漢肺炎疫情令英國私校被中資收購的速度加快。英國脫歐黨（Brexit Party）黨魁指，中共通過大型國際投資來主導全球經濟，甚至連文化層面都不能倖免地被影響，「政府必須醒悟並迅速行動」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：自稱親華派 約翰遜冀復經貿對話<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日郵報》前日報道，在武漢肺炎打擊下，英國多間私人學校入讀學生大跌，有寄宿學校去年的學生人數下跌35%，日間學生則下跌20%。在經營困難下，加快了中資集團收購英國私校速度，去年中資集團收購至少三間私校。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/00WS83nFUm0esNgtJ9v9Se5pTtI=/3870x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WWK2KF5KGVDQJNEVGR7K5ACRGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F00WS83nFUm0esNgtJ9v9Se5pTtI%3D%2F3870x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWWK2KF5KGVDQJNEVGR7K5ACRGI.jpg&h=cf674859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■邁重爾頓學院被中資「雅力教育集團」收購。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戴妃母校亦遭收購<br />\n<br />\n報道指，中資幾年前便開始收購英國私校。碧桂園集團聯席主席楊惠妍擔任董事長的「博實樂教育集團」自2018年起買下多間學校，包括百年傳統老校伯恩茅斯學校（Bournemouth Collegiate School），楊惠妍的父親楊。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國教育部發言人回應報道指，「私立學校的擁有人有提倡英國基本價值觀的要求，學校不能宣傳黨派政治觀點」。<br />\n<br />\n英國脫歐黨黨魁法拉奇（Nigel Farage）在《星期日郵報》撰文指，「。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陶傑：華人家長不會選<br />\n<br />\n熟悉英國的作家陶傑對本報表示，英國在失去殖民地和國內經濟疲弱的情況下，私校結業遲早也會出現，不過就算中資購入，若果學校交不出漂亮的成績單，依然沒有人會願意入讀，結局同樣是被淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n不少來自香港或中國大陸的學。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日郵報》/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v3G-pOOR4kWyNtIJE1D38oRrDBU=/3329x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SLNVSEKKLND6VFUJVIRPI45WYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv3G-pOOR4kWyNtIJE1D38oRrDBU%3D%2F3329x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSLNVSEKKLND6VFUJVIRPI45WYI.jpg&h=669cd6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■戴妃曾就讀的里德爾斯沃思堂預備學校已被孔裔國際教育集團收購。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fol7trlofpbpQKK3DnM0n29lmYg=/912x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DRAW5HMBEBCIRD5DLIHN7M7VTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffol7trlofpbpQKK3DnM0n29lmYg%3D%2F912x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDRAW5HMBEBCIRD5DLIHN7M7VTM.jpg&h=f2f371c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴妃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/26vSNnrIWQc_8eYFZcf4hjey3qQ=/2167x2248/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X3IC733WV5EILOWF2V3EOWUZXY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F26vSNnrIWQc_8eYFZcf4hjey3qQ%3D%2F2167x2248%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX3IC733WV5EILOWF2V3EOWUZXY.gif&h=f00df186&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41d66021e626354776383e99e83b9474bda8077f","tid":2419343,"uid":364767,"like":0,"